{
  "name": "TB — CRM Autopilot (leads → CRM + all emails)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## CRM Autopilot\nReplaces the old Lead Router — deactivate/delete that one.\n\nEvery submission from tbsol.net is handled automatically:\n• Website lead → SAVED INTO YOUR CRM (stage New, follow-up in 2 days) + email you\n• Client intake (/start) → email you + welcome email to the client\n• Support ticket → email you (urgent flagged) + confirmation to client\n• Portal signup → email you about the new prospect\n\n### Setup\n1. Run hq/automation-setup.sql in Supabase (one time).\n2. In **Save lead to CRM**: replace PASTE_SERVICE_KEY (both headers) with your Supabase service_role key (Supabase → Settings → API keys). It lives ONLY in n8n.\n3. Attach your email credential on the 6 Email nodes.\n4. Save → flip **Active**.",
        "height": 460,
        "width": 400
      },
      "id": "note1",
      "name": "Read me",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -180,
        40
      ]
    },
